# CORS proxy base URL — appended with the encoded target URL.
# Must be a full URL: start with https:// and end with the query parameter that
# carries the target (e.g. ?target=). A bare host like example.workers.dev is invalid.
# Leave empty for direct requests (same-origin or local dev).
# Example: VITE_API_PROXY_URL=https://only-tools-web.blackn.workers.dev?target=
